From Howard Berkey Subject Re Shipping a bike In article MELLON A Ted Lemon writes Can someone recommend how to ship a motorcycle from San Francisco to Seattle And how much might it cost I'd recommend that you hop on the back of it and cruise that's a really nice ride, if you choose your route with any care at all Shouldn't cost more than about in gas, and maybe a night's motel bill Yes Up the coast, over to Portland, then up I Really nice most of the way, and I'm sure there's even better ways Watch the weather, though I got about as good a drenching as possible in the Oregon coast range once Howard Berkey Help